name: Maya Gold Trading
description: Maya Gold Trading was founded in 2013 in Amsterdam, the Netherlands. We have experience supplying organic food products to partners in over 40 countries. We are an international importer and trader of organic food products. We provide a wide range of the finest organic products and ingredients sourced from the most sustainable sources. Organic Agave and Coconut products are our star products, but they are not the only ones! Our services cover the entire market, regardless of size, so let's talk about what we can do for you and your company.
